#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.choose.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.choose"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:1 of
msgid ""
"Construct a tensor from an index tensor and a set of tensors to choose "
"from."
msgstr "根据索引张量和一组可选张量构造一个新张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:3 of
msgid ""
"First of all, if confused or uncertain, definitely look at the Examples -"
" in its full generality, this function is less simple than it might seem "
"from the following code description (below ndi = `mt.lib.index_tricks`):"
msgstr ""
"首先，如果感到困惑或不确定，请务必查看示例——从下面的代码描述来看（以下 "
"ndi = `mt.lib.index_tricks`），此函数并不像表面上看起来那么简单："

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:8 of
msgid ""
"``mt.choose(a,c) == mt.array([c[a[I]][I] for I in "
"ndi.ndindex(a.shape)])``."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:10 of
msgid "But this omits some subtleties.  Here is a fully general summary:"
msgstr "但这忽略了一些细节。以下是一个完全通用的总结："

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:12 of
msgid ""
"Given an \"index\" tensor (`a`) of integers and a sequence of `n` tensors"
" (`choices`), `a` and each choice tensor are first broadcast, as "
"necessary, to tensors of a common shape; calling these *Ba* and "
"*Bchoices[i], i = 0,...,n-1* we have that, necessarily, ``Ba.shape == "
"Bchoices[i].shape`` for each `i`.  Then, a new array with shape "
"``Ba.shape`` is created as follows:"
msgstr ""
"给定一个整数“索引”张量 (`a`) 和 `n` 个张量的序列 (`choices`)，`a` 和"
"每个可选张量会根据需要进行广播，使其具有相同的形状；称这些广播后的张量为 "
"*Ba* 和 *Bchoices[i], i = 0,...,n-1*，则对于每个 `i`，必然有 ``Ba.shape ="
"= Bchoices[i].shape``。然后，将创建一个形状为 ``Ba.shape`` 的新数组，如下"
"所示："

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:19 of
msgid ""
"if ``mode=raise`` (the default), then, first of all, each element of `a` "
"(and thus `Ba`) must be in the range `[0, n-1]`; now, suppose that `i` "
"(in that range) is the value at the `(j0, j1, ..., jm)` position in `Ba` "
"- then the value at the same position in the new array is the value in "
"`Bchoices[i]` at that same position;"
msgstr ""
"如果 ``mode=raise``（默认值），则首先，`a`（因此也是 `Ba`）的每个元素都"
"必须在 `[0, n-1]` 范围内；现在，假设 `i`（在该范围内）是 `Ba` 中 `(j0, j1"
", ..., jm)` 位置的值——那么新数组中相同位置的值就是在 `Bchoices[i]` 中相同"
"位置的值；"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:25 of
msgid ""
"if ``mode=wrap``, values in `a` (and thus `Ba`) may be any (signed) "
"integer; modular arithmetic is used to map integers outside the range "
"`[0, n-1]` back into that range; and then the new array is constructed as"
" above;"
msgstr ""
"如果 ``mode=wrap``，`a`（因此也是 `Ba`）中的值可以是任意（有符号）整数；"
"使用模运算将范围外的整数映射回 `[0, n-1]` 范围内；然后按上述方式构造新"
"数组；"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:30 of
msgid ""
"if ``mode=clip``, values in `a` (and thus `Ba`) may be any (signed) "
"integer; negative integers are mapped to 0; values greater than `n-1` are"
" mapped to `n-1`; and then the new tensor is constructed as above."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``mode=clip``，`a`（因此也是 `Ba`）中的值可以是任意（有符号）整数；"
"负整数被映射为 0；大于 `n-1` 的值被映射为 `n-1`；然后按上述方式构造新张量"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:34 of
msgid ""
"This tensor must contain integers in `[0, n-1]`, where `n` is the number "
"of choices, unless ``mode=wrap`` or ``mode=clip``, in which cases any "
"integers are permissible."
msgstr ""
"此张量必须包含 `[0, n-1]` 范围内的整数，其中 `n` 是可选项的数量，除非 ``"
"mode=wrap`` 或 ``mode=clip``，在这种情况下允许任意整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:38 of
msgid ""
"Choice tensors. `a` and all of the choices must be broadcastable to the "
"same shape.  If `choices` is itself a tensor (not recommended), then its "
"outermost dimension (i.e., the one corresponding to ``choices.shape[0]``)"
" is taken as defining the \"sequence\"."
msgstr ""
"可选张量。`a` 和所有可选项必须能够广播到相同的形状。如果 `choices` 本身是"
"张量（不推荐），则其最外层维度（即对应于 ``choices.shape[0]`` 的维度）被"
"视为定义“序列”的维度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:43 of
msgid ""
"If provided, the result will be inserted into this tensor. It should be "
"of the appropriate shape and dtype."
msgstr "如果提供此参数，结果将被插入到该张量中。它应具有适当的形状和数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:46 of
msgid ""
"Specifies how indices outside `[0, n-1]` will be treated:    * 'raise' : "
"an exception is raised   * 'wrap' : value becomes value mod `n`   * "
"'clip' : values < 0 are mapped to 0, values > n-1 are mapped to n-1"
msgstr ""
"指定如何处理 `[0, n-1]` 范围之外的索引：    * 'raise' : 引发异常   * '"
"wrap' : 值变为值模 `n`   * 'clip' : 值 < 0 被映射为 0，值 > n-1 被映射为 "
"n-1"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:47 of
msgid "Specifies how indices outside `[0, n-1]` will be treated:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:49 of
msgid "'raise' : an exception is raised"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:50 of
msgid "'wrap' : value becomes value mod `n`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:51 of
msgid "'clip' : values < 0 are mapped to 0, values > n-1 are mapped to n-1"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:54 of
msgid "**merged_array** -- The merged result."
msgstr "**merged_array** -- 合并后的结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:57 of
msgid ""
"shape mismatch: If `a` and each choice tensor are not all broadcastable "
"to the same     shape."
msgstr "形状不匹配：如果 `a` 和每个可选张量不能全部广播到相同的形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:61 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Tensor.choose`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:62 of
msgid "equivalent method"
msgstr "等效方法"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:65 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.choose.choose:66 of
msgid ""
"To reduce the chance of misinterpretation, even though the following "
"\"abuse\" is nominally supported, `choices` should neither be, nor be "
"thought of as, a single tensor, i.e., the outermost sequence-like "
"container should be either a list or a tuple."
msgstr ""
"为了减少误解的可能性，尽管以下“滥用”在名义上是支持的，但 `choices` "
"既不应是一个张量，也不应被视为一个张量，即最外层的序列类容器应为列表或"
"元组。"

